        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for article by G. H. Lewes ["Mr Darwin’s hypotheses, pt 1", <hi rend="italic">Fortn. Rev.</hi> n.s. 3 (1868): 353–73]. Comments on article.</p> 
            <p>Describes hybridisation experiment carried out on rabbits and hares by Dr Conrad.</p> 
<p>Encloses description of <hi rend="italic">Monera</hi></p> 
            <p>and a phylogenetic table of vertebrates.</p>
            <p>Mentions work on Medusae.</p>
            <p>The controversy over CD in Germany.</p>
        </abstract>
